This is the area corresponding to the South Connecting Sea and it is situated directly south west the naval base. The second and third map are the rough equivalent of [[Phase 1/World 1|Phase 1]] 1-5 and 1-6.<br>
There is one repair dock on this hexagon and is expandable up to two.<br>
:Clearing the first map of this area (V9-1), alongside [[Kancolle Kai:Sandbox/Area 8#/V8-1|V8-1]] gives access to [[KanColle Kai:Sandbox/Area 11#/V11-1|V11-1]] ('''中部西海域''').
:Fully clearing this area gives access to [[KanColle Kai:Sandbox/Area 2#/V2-1|V2-1]] ('''南西諸島海域''').

